          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features03\" group=\"Features\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n    <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"cardsWidth\">\n      <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n      <option value=\"6\">2</option>\n      <option value=\"4\">3</option>\n      <option value=\"3\" selected>4</option>\n    </select>\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showSubtitle\" title=\"Subtitle\">\n    <header>Cards</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"autoSize\" title=\"Auto Size\" checked>\n    <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageHeight\" title=\"Height\" min=\"1\" max=\"5\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\" condition=\"autoSize\"><input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Spacing\" name=\"spacing\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showText\" title=\"Text\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButtons\" title=\"Buttons\" checked>\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" parallax name=\"bg\" required>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n    </fieldset>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#edefeb\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center mb-5\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-head\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n          <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n            <b>What&#x27;s Happening</b>\n          </h4>\n          <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mt-4 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n            To add more cards, hover on a card and click 'Add items'\n          </h5>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"item features-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}} active\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"item-img mb-3\">\n            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/photo-1578231177134-f1bbe379b054.jpeg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title=\"\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"item-content align-left\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n            <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n              <b>Live Jazz Night: The Blue Notes</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">October 26</p>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Get ready to swing! The Blue Notes are bringing their soulful melodies for an unforgettable evening of pure jazz.</p>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons=\"\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href=\"\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Feast</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"item-img mb-3\">\n            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/photo-1628613550014-d89ec27d7667.jpeg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title=\"\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"item-content align-left\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n            <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-2 mt-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n              <b>Wine Tasting: Italian Delights</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">November 10</p>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Sip and savor the finest wines from Italy&#x27;s most celebrated regions. A true oenophile&#x27;s dream.</p>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons=\"\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href=\"\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Feast</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"item-img mb-3\">\n            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/photo-1593536488177-1eb3c2d4e3d2.jpeg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title=\"\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"item-content align-left\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n            <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-2 mt-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n              <b>Open Mic Comedy Hour</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">November 18</p>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Prepare for belly laughs! Our stage is open to aspiring comedians. Who knows, you might discover the next big star.</p>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons=\"\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href=\"\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Feast</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"item-img mb-3\">\n            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/photo-1726873800099-53f5496281e0.jpeg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title=\"\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"item-content align-left\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n            <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-2 mt-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n              <b>Chef&#x27;s Table: Seasonal Menu</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">December 01</p>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">An exclusive dining experience. Join our Head Chef for a multi-course tasting menu showcasing the freshest seasonal ingredients.</p>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons=\"\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href=\"\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Feast</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n",
